    "Answer Here-Positive Business Impact: Yes. Understanding volume trends helps in algorithmic trading and risk management. For institutional investors or Tesla's treasury, knowing when liquidity spikes allows them to execute large block trades with minimal market impact (lower slippage). It also aids in timing market volatility, as volume expansion usually precedes massive price breakouts.\n",
