    "Answer Here.A line chart of sorted data (plt.plot(np.sort(df['Open']))) was selected because it functions similarly to a Cumulative Distribution Function (CDF) plot, which is excellent for analyzing the overall distribution, floor-to-ceiling range, and acceleration profile of an asset's price.\n",
    "\n",
